      <title>诺和诺德的 Wegovy 在中国获批用于减肥</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/novo-nordisk-s-wegovy-approved-in-china-for-weight-loss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国已批准诺和诺德公司（Novo Nordisk A/S）的重磅药物威戈维（Wegovy）用于慢性体重管理，为世界第二大经济体的下一代减肥药物拉开了竞争的序幕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/novo-nordisk-s-wegovy-approved-in-china-for-weight-loss</guid>
